# r75 Benchmark

This folder contains the scripts and output files for the r75 missing-modality PBMC RNA-ATAC integration benchmark.

In the r75 setting, only 25% of cells remain paired, while the remaining cells are split into RNA-only and ATAC-only groups. This setting was used to compare the robustness of MultiVI, GLUE and MOFA+ under simulated missing-modality conditions.

