## Method folders

### `r75_MULTIVI/`

Contains the script and outputs for preparing the r75 dataset and running MultiVI under the r75 setting.

Main files:

```text
prepare_r75_data.py
r75_modality_status.csv
run_multivi_r75.py
multivi_r75_latent.csv
multivi_r75_latent.h5ad
```

### `r75_GLUE/`

Contains the script and outputs for running GLUE under the r75 setting.

Main files:

```text
r75_run_glue.py
glue_r75_latent.csv
glue_r75_latent.h5ad
```

### `r75_MOFA/`

Contains the script and outputs for running MOFA+ under the r75 setting.

Main files:

```text
r75_run_mofa.py
mofa_r75_latent.csv
mofa_r75_latent.h5ad
```

## Script-output summary

| Script | Main outputs |
|---|---|
| `r75_MULTIVI/prepare_r75_data.py` | `r75_modality_status.csv` |
| `r75_MULTIVI/run_multivi_r75.py` | `multivi_r75_latent.csv`, `multivi_r75_latent.h5ad` |
| `r75_GLUE/r75_run_glue.py` | `glue_r75_latent.csv`, `glue_r75_latent.h5ad` |
| `r75_MOFA/r75_run_mofa.py` | `mofa_r75_latent.csv`, `mofa_r75_latent.h5ad` |
| `run_r75_benchmark.py` | `strict_r75_benchmark_metrics.csv`, `strict_r75_celltypewise_knn.csv`, immune programme smoothness CSV files |
| `generate_r75_figures.py` | r75 UMAPs and benchmark figures |

## Benchmark outputs

| File | Description |
|---|---|
| `strict_r75_benchmark_metrics.csv` | Main r75 benchmark metrics for MultiVI, GLUE and MOFA+ |
| `strict_r75_celltypewise_knn.csv` | Cell-type-wise KNN purity results |
| `r75_ari_summary.csv` | Supplementary ARI clustering-agreement results |
| `r75_direct_rna_to_atac_agreement_K15_summary.csv` | Direct RNA-to-ATAC agreement summary using K = 15 |
| `r75_direct_rna_to_atac_agreement_K15_celltypewise.csv` | Cell-type-wise direct RNA-to-ATAC agreement results |
| `r75_immune_programme_smoothness_metrics.csv` | Overall immune programme smoothness results |
| `r75_immune_programme_smoothness_by_programme.csv` | Immune programme smoothness results separated by programme |

## Metrics

The r75 benchmark mainly used:

- NMI
- Balanced silhouette score
- Balanced KNN purity
- Cross-modal KNN purity
- Cross-modal cell-type agreement
- KNN modality entropy
- Same-modality enrichment
- Direct RNA-to-ATAC agreement
- ARI
- Immune programme smoothness

## Notes

- `r75_modality_status.csv` records whether each cell is paired, RNA-only or ATAC-only.
- The same marker-based PBMC cell-type annotation was used across all methods.
- Leiden clusters were generated separately for each method.
- UMAPs are used for visualization and should not be compared only by shape.
- The r75 benchmark was compared with the paired benchmark to assess robustness under missing-modality conditions.
